    <item>
      <title>能源交易商 Mercuria 连续第三年盈利逾 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mercuria-made-over-2-billion-in-third-year-of-bumper-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，摩科瑞能源集团有限公司（Mercuria Energy Group Ltd）的利润略高于 20 亿美元，尽管大宗商品盈利热潮开始消退，但对于这家能源交易商来说，这仍然是一个丰厚的业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mercuria-made-over-2-billion-in-third-year-of-bumper-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 18:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
