      <title>米勒政府被指控操纵大豆河升级拍卖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/milei-government-accused-of-skewing-auction-to-upgrade-soy-river</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项期待已久的招标受到了猛烈的批评，其中包括两名竞标者指责阿根廷政府偏袒现任承包商，该招标旨在升级一条主要水道，每年该水道向全球市场运送价值数百亿美元的农作物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/milei-government-accused-of-skewing-auction-to-upgrade-soy-river</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 18:11:50 GMT</pubDate>
